This is vividpup built with woof CE and using ubuntu 14.10 vivid vervet packages. 

 Kernel 3.19.5_PAE (built using stemsees sukk-1.7) 
 jwm & rox, palemoon, thunderbird, libreoffice, gimp, deadbeef, avidemux, simplescreenrecorder, coquillo, smilla enlarger, tixati, vlc, QT, python, pidgin, sticky Jwm, packit, uextract, p7zip, pupsysinfo, pupclockset, urxvtcontrol, find'n'run 
 plus the usual suspects. 

 wallpaper by futwerk 

 
 A modern multi-core PC with more than 2gb of ram is recommended 
 
It's a big one! 432mb
